---
import TuiBox from '../TuiBox.astro';
---
<div class="term-pane-header">
  <div class="tui-panel-header"><span>PIPELINES</span></div>
</div>
<div class="term-pane" style="overflow-y:auto">
<div style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto">
  <h2 class="section-header fg-pink">// agent pipeline orchestration //</h2>

  <!-- Step flow -->
  <p class="fg-comment" style="font-size:11px;margin-bottom:8px">// step flow</p>
  <pre class="fg-purple" style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:24px">
&#9484;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9488;
&#9474;   PROVIDER   &#9474;  executor: claude
&#9474;  (claude)    &#9474;  model: sonnet-4-6
&#9492;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9524;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9496;
       &#9474; <span class="fg-comment">output: string</span>
       &#9660;
&#9484;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9516;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9488;
&#9474;    PLUGIN    &#9474;  plugin: jq
&#9474;   (jq)       &#9474;  input: string
&#9492;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9524;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9496;
       &#9474; <span class="fg-comment">output: object</span>
       &#9660;
&#9484;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9516;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9488;
&#9474;    PLUGIN    &#9474;  plugin: write
&#9474;   (write)    &#9474;  path: ./out/result.json
&#9492;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9472;&#9496;</pre>

  <!-- Example switcher -->
  <div class="pipeline-tabs" role="tablist">
    <button class="pipeline-tab active" data-example="0" onclick="PipelineExamples.show(0)">code-review</button>
    <button class="pipeline-tab" data-example="1" onclick="PipelineExamples.show(1)">brain-loop</button>
    <button class="pipeline-tab" data-example="2" onclick="PipelineExamples.show(2)">gh-triage</button>
    <span class="fg-comment" style="font-size:10px;padding:6px 8px;align-self:center">[tab] cycle &nbsp; [r] replay</span>
  </div>
  <pre id="pipeline-example" class="pipeline-example-pre"></pre>

  <TuiBox title="OPERATOR NOTES">
    <div class="tui-box-row">
      <div class="tui-box-label fg-pink">typed steps</div>
      <div class="tui-box-desc">Each step declares input: and output: schemas, enforced at runtime. No silent type mismatches.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tui-box-row">
      <div class="tui-box-label fg-pink">interpolation</div>
      <div class="tui-box-desc">Reference any prior step's output with <span class="fg-yellow">&#123;&#123;steps.&lt;id&gt;.output&#125;&#125;</span>. Chain models into tools freely.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tui-box-row">
      <div class="tui-box-label fg-pink">brain context</div>
      <div class="tui-box-desc">Brain context is injected automatically. Prompt your model to emit a <span class="fg-cyan">&lt;brain&gt;</span> block — gl1tch extracts and stores it for later steps.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tui-box-row">
      <div class="tui-box-label fg-pink">on_failure</div>
      <div class="tui-box-desc">Recovery steps suppress the run-level error on success. Pipelines fail gracefully.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tui-box-row">
      <div class="tui-box-label fg-pink">providers</div>
      <div class="tui-box-desc">claude, ollama, gemini, github-copilot, opencode — or any sidecar plugin. Mix in one pipeline.</div>
    </div>
  </TuiBox>

  <p style="color:var(--comment);font-size:11px;margin-top:16px">
    <span class="fg-yellow">&rarr;</span> Press <span class="fg-yellow">4</span> for plugins &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
    <span class="fg-yellow">9</span> for brain/docs &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;
    <span class="fg-yellow">tab</span> to cycle &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; <span class="fg-yellow">r</span> to replay
  </p>
</div>
</div>

<style>
.pipeline-tabs {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0;
  margin-bottom: 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--comment);
}

.pipeline-tab {
  background: none;
  border: none;
  border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
  color: var(--comment);
  font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  font-size: 11px;
  padding: 4px 12px 6px;
  cursor: pointer;
  margin-bottom: -1px;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.pipeline-tab:hover {
  color: var(--fg);
}

.pipeline-tab.active {
  color: var(--fg);
  border-bottom-color: var(--pink);
}

.pipeline-example-pre {
  font-size: 11px;
  line-height: 1.65;
  color: var(--fg);
  height: 340px;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 10px 0 0;
  margin: 0 0 24px;
}
</style>
